## Objective: Generate unified 
design tokens and styles from a page screenshot or style guide.

## Input: {{SCREENSHOT_URL}} 、the add picture or design description.

## Output: /packages/tokens, /packages/ui, brand style documentation.

## Example Usage
```
/UI 根据”蔚蓝+科技为样式“生成 Web 与 React Native 统一设计令牌（色板/字号/间距/阴影/圆角），产出 tokens 与说明。
```
## Output
- /packages/tokens/tokens.json (color palette, font sizes, spacing, shadows, rounded corners, component dimensions)
- /packages/ui/* (Cross-platform components like Button, Input, Card, Sheet, etc.)
- /docs/UI_GUIDE.md (Reuse across Web/Native/Weixin)

## Key Points
- React: CSS vars + Tailwind (optional)
- RN/Expo: StyleSheet + token adaptation
- Weixin: app.wxss mapping with custom components